Privacy Policy for LinkFlow
1. Introduction

LinkFlow ("we," "our," or "pudding.dev") values your privacy. This policy explains how we handle information when you use our Chrome Extension.

2. Data Collection and Usage

No Personal Data Collection: LinkFlow does not collect, store, or transmit any personal identification information.

Local Processing Only: All link extraction and tab-opening processes occur locally on your device. We do not have access to the text you paste or the URLs you open.

No Third-Party Sharing: Since we do not collect data, no information is shared with third parties.

3. Permissions Justification

Tabs: Used solely to open the extracted URLs in new browser tabs.

ClipboardRead: Used only to allow the "Paste" functionality within the extension interface.

4. Contact

For any questions regarding this policy, please contact us at your dedicated email address.
